{"tid":500914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★移民Vs港樓  一幅圖睇晒歐洲投資移民門檻","createTime":"2017-12-16T09:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T12:00:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d6b67aa85229dc2230677173ff14298c452e48","tid":500914,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1735000/1736269/europe_thumb_20170328_c_v2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1735000%2F1736269%2Feurope_thumb_20170328_c_v2_1024.jpg&h=71491d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日移民又成為話題，但傳統的英美澳加投資移民門檻高，一般香港人未必有資格申請。到底移民到歐洲還有甚麼選擇？<br />\n<br />\nTOPick向移民顧問關景鴻查詢，他指部分歐洲國家可選擇買樓作投資移民，較有保障：<br />\n<br />\n1. 英語國家首選愛爾蘭<br />\n<br />\n關景鴻指，愛爾蘭為英語國家，投資移民門檻亦較英國低，申請人需證明有200萬歐元資產，其中要投資100萬歐元（約844萬港元），而英國則需200萬英鎊，約1,940萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，愛爾蘭不能以買樓作投資移民，雖然官方沒有列明需投資的實際項目，但投資在福利房（公屋）及老人院等社會福利項目可被優先考慮。<br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭要求申請者每年在愛爾蘭居住7日，較英國的9個月門檻低。<br />\n<br />\n2. 葡萄牙樓價低<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙是其中一個可買樓移民的國家，需50萬歐元（約422萬港元），可購買商業樓宇或住宅、甚至投資地皮，需投資5年。<br />\n<br />\n關景鴻指，50萬歐元可在葡萄牙市區購買2,000至2,500呎的別墅。買樓的用途並沒有明確限制，自住、放租或空置均可。申請者需在第1年住滿7天，並在以後每2年住滿14天。<br />\n<br />\n【延伸閱讀】 想離開香港？一圖睇晒投資移民門檻<br />\n<br />\n3. 西班牙樓價較高<br />\n<br />\n西班牙同樣可以買樓移民，其門檻同為50萬歐元（約422萬港元）及投資5年，50萬歐元可在巴塞羅那或馬德里等地區買入約800至1,000呎的2房至3房單位。另外，亦要每次續期時到西班牙一次，但沒有居住要求。<br />\n<br />\n4. 意大利需約30萬歐元<br />\n<br />\n意大利買樓投資移民需約30萬歐元（約211萬港元），同樣為投資5年。關景鴻指，意大利可以30萬歐元購買約2,000呎獨立屋，亦為不錯的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n申請永久居留權的人士需每半年到一次意大利，並有獨立穩定的經濟來源，非工資收入不低於每年3.1萬歐元（約26萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n5. 希臘經濟低迷<br />\n<br />\n相比之下，希臘買樓投資移民的門檻更低，約25萬歐元（約211萬港元）即可，可買到2,000至2,500呎別墅。但關景鴻指，希臘的經濟低迷，二手市場不活躍，及後想放售或有難度。他建議先考慮愛爾蘭、西班牙及葡萄牙等國家才考慮希臘。<br />\n<br />\n6. 南歐國家馬爾他<br />\n<br />\n馬爾他為南歐的微型國家，佔地不足香港的8分之一，人口約有42萬，投資門檻為35萬歐元（約295萬港元）及5年；但同時要以15萬歐元（約126萬）購買馬爾他政府債劵及向馬爾他國家發展及社會基金捐贈約65萬歐元（約548萬港元），合共約115萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n移民馬爾他可取得歐盟護照及歐盟公民身份，有免費教育等福利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1736269/想出走歐洲？一幅圖睇晒歐洲投資移民門檻?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1736269%2F%E6%83%B3%E5%87%BA%E8%B5%B0%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%EF%BC%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%85%E5%9C%96%E7%9D%87%E6%99%92%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b4f60451\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1736269/想出走歐洲？一幅圖睇晒歐洲投資移民門檻?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"31c22a9a6c62399bd9992e813898c09c1eac174b","tid":500914,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce3736e93d72851f01dc1025563d68e53fb33d1","tid":500914,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffccdd60fc28e2d6fdb2bf1c59c6f9880151517","tid":500914,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"謝"},{"pid":"812eb70cf137dd9f77b58a095d8675ba94da9170","tid":500914,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:44:50.000Z","msg":"一千萬買hk空氣樓最<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404eab4822aaa2df19583a1c3f296a395627bf4b","tid":500914,"uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/214657_1f21583fd587d798f30b64294645295f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F214657_1f21583fd587d798f30b64294645295f.jpg&h=40ba5af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"413eb98b433678d7cee477d311529cdf9f2e3718","tid":500914,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/215240_19e202463712c0a721a36c92ee33c1f8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F215240_19e202463712c0a721a36c92ee33c1f8.jpeg&h=729de735&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"042aa387c640f724890fae749f15754215a4bb1f","tid":500914,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"老貓移去邊?"},{"pid":"7c9d3cfd0b14df14c1519a09026e52213d1086fd","tid":500914,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"35d74c2310123ed8b084f8a1bfe973ff761f301a","tid":500914,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:00:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f01ef2a43703e1acfcccd4ced9eac60f1d78baf2","tid":500914,"uid":37735,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"其實對好多人來講<br />\n<br />\n個重點是香港堆廢柴係歐洲，美國 搵唔返香港個收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n種族<br />\n語言<br />\n關係網<br />\n都有<br />\n<br />\n00打後 一堆人回流 <br />\n(撈唔惦就話人歧視自己 一堆賤種狗)<br />\n<br />\n就用保險，金融來講<br />\n語音能力連人地掃街果件都好過你 <br />\n人際關係網又無<br />\n點sell service 出去比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又好像何志平 呢堆<br />\n係香港打橫來行  係歐美一早被人捉鬼左"},{"pid":"0f8ba968ce1de69843da1d52ba26adcfccafc9a7","tid":500914,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老貓移去邊?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/220413_280ea4689b47a225fb9db6c66864ac0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F220413_280ea4689b47a225fb9db6c66864ac0a.jpg&h=4cae0d81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10b49775f5559b21ddc288a3839fceacdfc57a6d","tid":500914,"uid":37735,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實對好多人來講<br />\n<br />\n個重點是香港堆廢柴係歐洲，美國 搵唔返香港個收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n種族<br />\n語言<br />\n關係網<br />\n都有<br />\n<br />\n00打後 一堆人回流 <br />\n(撈唔惦就話人歧視自己 一堆賤種狗)<br />\n<br />\n就用保險，金融來講<br />\n語音能力連人地掃街果件都好過你 <br />\n人際關係網又無<br />\n點sell service 出去比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又好像何志平 呢堆<br />\n係香港打橫來行  係歐美一早被人捉鬼左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n澳洲有條友 收支那黑金<br />\n成個黨要同佢割席  最多比少少面子  要佢自己走(因為人地選票 民意 投出來 <br />\n<br />\n香港果種死唔辭職 根本唔work<br />\n自己唔走 等住被人踢出去)<br />\n假博士 <br />\n鉛水<br />\n死都唔走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n總之個關鍵是支那為左統戰香港<br />\n貼左好多錢 令香港好多人 收入遠高於其實際能力  呢班人  出到外國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d625927fd3b707c06e2e84bb3d613ee0d4ee6e6e","tid":500914,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老貓移去邊?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/220413_280ea4689b47a225fb9db6c66864ac0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F220413_280ea4689b47a225fb9db6c66864ac0a.jpg&h=4cae0d81&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你有無12個BITCOIN?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171011/57317087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171011%2F57317087&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=7f090d47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171011%2F57317087&h=5ce7001f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171011/57317087</a><br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，港人想去的地南太平洋島國瓦努阿圖，宣佈接受比特幣Bitcoin支付投資移民，換言之只需40多個比特幣，就可以買到一個國籍。<br />\n<br />\n瓦努阿圖此舉是全球首個可以接受比特幣購買國籍的國家，根據瓦努阿圖20萬美元移民經費作計算，比特幣境外現價報逾4,800美元，故以42個比特幣，就可以移民到這個快樂的國度。<br />\n<br />\n雖然中國禁比特幣交易後，曾令其價格一沉。不過，自日前突破4,600美元後，昨日一度升至4,854美元的逾1個月高位，急挫後收復失地。"},{"pid":"614eb3fbefc275d077ca9aa231dd2ffc611c7f15","tid":500914,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab279d2e38f2e91ccb9a62ca9883b1437885d233","tid":500914,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實對好多人來講<br />\n<br />\n個重點是香港堆廢柴係歐洲，美國 搵唔返香港個收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n種族<br />\n語言<br />\n關係網<br />\n都有<br />\n<br />\n00打後 一堆人回流 <br />\n(撈唔惦就話人歧視自己 一堆賤種狗)<br />\n<br />\n就用保險，金融來講<br />\n語音能力連人地掃街果件都好過你 <br />\n人際關係網又無<br />\n點sell service 出去比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又好像何志平 呢堆<br />\n係香港打橫來行  係歐美一早被人捉鬼左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝志峰咪係囉<br />\n移左去加拿大, 洗晒D錢, 無計死返黎香港<br />\n<br />\n佢係加拿大, 坐食山崩"},{"pid":"38c6bb1e9125e8de4fe79b757b12b8ed582fa5f2","tid":500914,"uid":88252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"個個國家都寫每年最少住幾日 <br />\n根本唔係真心走果隻啦只係想留條後路"},{"pid":"2af744a8f7c142933f8bc737d18ccfa2bc9253bc","tid":500914,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"移去台灣都好危險<br />\n<br />\n係外國(支那friend國)比拉, 直接押返支那<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6c5bb82ca5c6d1a0cc9f5b4ccb181b78376e23","tid":500914,"uid":148639,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d90711c4389c685c38f4a00df663a1e4e879fa62","tid":500914,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"應該爭取 BNO + IELTS 8.5分 以上 移民英國打個折"},{"pid":"12c64330cebfb014781302bdc6ffcb664cfcbe67","tid":500914,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/214657_1f21583fd587d798f30b64294645295f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F214657_1f21583fd587d798f30b64294645295f.jpg&h=40ba5af3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n厄瓜多爾19萬<br />\n攞個護照脱支那籍"},{"pid":"25c6277809c5845883862cd9f560ad7198045704","tid":500914,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"南美洲的厄瓜多爾條件容易許多，其更曾被美國《國際生活》（International Living）評為最佳退休宜居地之一。申請人需在當地銀行存入至少2.5萬美元（約新台幣76萬元），若要攜帶家眷，每人只要加500美元（約新台幣1萬5000元），<span style=\"color: red;\">成功申請後可獲永久居留權</span>，住滿3年就能入籍。"},{"pid":"cc7158d34e5ac18cab0b4fecbfc179d963373c45","tid":500914,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老貓移去邊?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/220413_280ea4689b47a225fb9db6c66864ac0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F220413_280ea4689b47a225fb9db6c66864ac0a.jpg&h=4cae0d81&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你鬼有錢移"},{"pid":"8b55125a8fc03b6cf689913e32fb4c993bfe2071","tid":500914,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老貓移去邊?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/220413_280ea4689b47a225fb9db6c66864ac0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: